title: IAA Tonight | NFL Trade Deadline Winners & Losers AND The Nets To Hire Ime Udoka?
description: The NFL trade deadline day was the most active its ever been and included Bradley Chubb, T.J. Hockensen, and Nyheim Hines on the move while Brandin Cooks and Kareem Hunt stay put. LeSean McCoy, Leger Douzable, and Brandon Flowers discuss those moves, and the Brooklyn Nets and Steve Nash mutually parting ways and suspended Boston Celtics head coach Ime Udoka possibly being his replacement.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, LeSean McCoy, Brandon Flowers)
